summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing negotiation for and purchase required for the South Victor Street Sanitary Sewer Project in portions of the Northeast one-quarter of the Southwest one-quarter of the Northeast one-quarter and the Northwest one-quarter of Section 3, Township 23N, Range 4E, W.M. together with certain temporary construction easements on properties abutting Beacon Avenue South from South Gazelle Street to the South City Limits and abutting Ryan Way South from Empire Way South to South 107th Street and making an appropriation from the Municipal Sewerage 1971 Construction Fund therefor.
